(19, 1, '2020-01-28 09:49:44', '2020-01-28 09:49:44', 'OUR APPROACHBecause we work with CARE in creating high quality MASS CRAFTSMANSHIP by using our unique PRANDA PROCESS,\nwe are THE ARCHITECTURE OF CRAFTSMANSHIP who brings in devotion to every step of craftsmanshipand this is our IDENTITY.				\n										<img width=\"525\" height=\"350\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Care-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Care-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Care-300x200.jpg 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Care-768x512.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Care-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Care-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n			<h2>CARE</h2>		\n		<p>At Pranda, we work with care. Our way of working from the heart forms the ties of relationships that bond us with our stakeholders. Our products are the results of our devotion to details and our commitment to our business partners and ultimately the consumers. That is why we produce only quality jewelry, which shows our heart and care in every piece. </p>		\n			<h2>Mass Craftsmanship</h2>		\n		<p>Over the past 40 years, we are the leading manufacturer of fine jewelry at the craftsmanship-level that can be accessible to majority of the people. To create large quantity creative crafts with consistently high quality, we combine our heart with our skills and expertises pioneering the term Mass Craftsmanship.</p>		\n										<img width=\"200\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Craftman-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Craftman-200x300.jpg 200w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Craftman-683x1024.jpg 683w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Craftman-768x1152.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Craftman-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Craftman-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Craftman-scaled.jpg 1707w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n										<img width=\"525\" height=\"350\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Process-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Process-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Process-300x200.jpg 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Process-768x512.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Process-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Process-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n			<h2>Pranda Process</h2>		\n		<p>The important strategy is for our jewelry to deliver the dream to our consumers throughly. We owe our success to the Pranda Process  a unique systematic management style with seven steps to excellence  transforming our business partners dream to reality, and most importantly- commercially viable in large quantity.</p>		\n			<h2>Our 7 Units Process</h2>		\n			<h2>1.</h2>		\n										<img width=\"525\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1024x575.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1024x575.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-300x168.jpg 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-768x431.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-1536x862.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1-2048x1150.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n			<h2>Market Intelligence</h2>		\n		<p>We extensively study on various trends in jewelry industry and consumer behavior to best acquiring the right marketing information for best decisions to serve our clients.</p>', 'OUR APPROACH', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-approach', '', '', '2020-01-29 04:49:50', '2020-01-29 04:49:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=19', 0, 'page', '', 0),
