(183, 1, '2020-01-29 03:50:18', '2020-01-29 03:50:18', 'Responsible Jewellery Council				\n			<h2>PRANDA GROUP ARE OFFICALLY CERTIFIED AS A RJC MEMBER</h2>		\n		<p>   Bangkok, Thailand, March 2018: Pranda Group, Thailands leading fine jewellery manufacturer, has recently been certified as a member of the Responsible Jewellery Council or RJC with a certification period of 3 years from 23 February 2018  23 February 2021.</p>		\n										<img width=\"525\" height=\"381\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/RJC-Certification-Logo-EU-Pranda-Jewelry-Public-Company-Limited-768x557.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/RJC-Certification-Logo-EU-Pranda-Jewelry-Public-Company-Limited-768x557.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/RJC-Certification-Logo-EU-Pranda-Jewelry-Public-Company-Limited-300x217.jpg 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/RJC-Certification-Logo-EU-Pranda-Jewelry-Public-Company-Limited-1024x742.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/RJC-Certification-Logo-EU-Pranda-Jewelry-Public-Company-Limited-1536x1113.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/RJC-Certification-Logo-EU-Pranda-Jewelry-Public-Company-Limited-2048x1485.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"100vw\" />											\n		<p>  On making the announcement, Mr. Decha Nuntanajareonkul, Executive Director, on behalf of the Social Management Representative (SMR), for Pranda Group, commented: The benefits that the company gain from RJC certification is to increase customer confidence in partnering with the Pranda group companies. The RJC is a whole-of-supply-chain standard initiative, and certifies a commitment to the implementation of responsible business practices throughout. Furthermore, Pranda affirms that the RJC has become an essential standard for the international jewellery sector. With this certification Pranda believe its a great opportunity to gain more customers worldwide with the accreditation building trust and confidence in the Pranda Group.</p>', 'Responsible Jewellery Council', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'responsible-jewellery-council', '', '', '2020-01-29 04:13:19', '2020-01-29 04:13:19', '', 8, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=183', 0, 'page', '', 0),
